title: 820-2530-a no PM_SLP_S4_L
message:
Green light is nothing to do with PPBUS_G3H ..... Unless I am just reading your post wrong.

Green light is PP3V42. It's a data line, so "logic level" which = 0 ~ 5V which is why 3V42 line is used.
PPBUS_G3H can be 0V and you'll still have 3V42 green / orange light... Providing the pull ups are in value and the SMC is working.

Post values, they can't help you without values ;)
